<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=H._H._Holmes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/3141999" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/3141999" rel="nofollow">Barclay &amp; Co. 1890. <i>Holmes, the arch fiend, or: A carnival of crime. The life, trial, confession and execution of H.H. Holmes. Twenty-seven lives sacrificed to this monstrous ogre's insatiable appetite</i>. Cincinnati: Barclay &amp; Co.</a></li>
